node.content:
["Police say State Highway 1 has reopened south of Foxton following a crash on the Manawat\u016b River bridge.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Earlier this afternoon, the road was blocked due to a crash on the bridge over the Manuwatu River which was reported shortly after 3pm.", "In a statement, Police said 4 vehicles were involved in the crash.", "Minor injuries were treated at the scene by St John Ambulance."]
